{"type": "article", "id": 21800, "title": "Bamboo charger by Zhang Jintian", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-03T08:14:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125719LpuTscGqvbHMzZPn.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一款集充电器、插头转换器、电筒于一身的智能工具，它们被设计在了 4 个竹节里。每一小节都可以打开，有四种不一样的接口，其中，最下面的底座的插头是活动式的 BS（british standard ）插头。此外，最上面的小圆灯可以单独拔下来作为小夜灯，非常适合旅行时使用。竹节的外形增加了一份清秀感，但产品目前还是一个概念。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide medium-insert-active\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125717hxlsN6HMeJ8GiW71.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125717EuVTWQmPYHhalbMc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"dragged\" style=\"height: 193px; width: 375px; left: 414px; top: 544px;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125718J1ADPxsHSEKh8jgC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125718lKnFwbhsv08Zpdyr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125719nesQ4kIcd53TWUHh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72380952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}